creator: Nitin Trehan
descriptionHtml:
Picture Your Travel is a Social Travel App, where your friends, family and peers come together to generate organic & trustworthy content, helping you enhance your travelplanning experience.

A picture based platform that binds ‘Trust &Travel’ like none other.


Picture

Don’t you hate it when planning your vacation becomes a task?
Surfing multiple travel sites and still no trustworthy travel advisor?
Imagine a platform where you and your friends can share your best travel discoveries which are real and authentic.
PYT lets you build an exclusive travelnetwork where the information is pooled in by your family and friends.Thus, infusing trust and credibility into your travel plans.

Plan

On our discovery page you’ll find plenty of visuals, superbly curated according to destinations discovered by your “SocialTravelNetwork”. Being your personal travel planner, we help you get a better insight on any vacation that inspires you. Our Location information page shows ‘travelreviews’, ‘nearby places’ and more pictures of places you like. Thus, extending your scope of gathering information and organising your trips by easily adding any location to your travel plan.


Post

Share your best ‘Globe Trotting Experiences’ on PYT and become a ‘Travel Influencer’ to the people you love and trust. Geotag your discoveries and assign appropriate Interest categories to them. We will then curate all your precious travel memories into a WorldTravel Album, specific to locations and travel dates.


How it works ?

1. Explore upto 5 destinations through country or city specific travel search.
2. Create your very own SocailTravel Network.
3. Invite your family and friends for trustworthy travelrecommendations.
4. Choose upto 16 Interest categories and we will create a personalized experience for you.
5. Get inspired by what your friends share and add them to your travelplanner.
6. Add Geotags to your discoveries and post them to create your travelbook.
descriptionShort: PYT is a social travel network that lets you Picture, Plan and Post your travel.

title: Picture Your Travel

creator: PYT Technologies Pvt. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
PYT is an ecosystem for travellers that helps them discover, plan/book, experience & share their journeys, from the comfort of their mobile device. A travel Super App that merges trust & convenience in a seamless manner and stays with the traveller through their journey, like a personal travel butler.

PYT was founded with the vision to bring the travellers digital journey on a ‘Single Trustworthy Platform’ where travellers, travel influencers and businesses share authentic and actionable information, co-exist, and prosper.

With its unique Word-of-Mouth social commerce model, PYT rewards travellers directly for influencing sales. A truly democratic travel world, that makes travel rewarding!

Since our start, we have been working towards Our mission to ‘Disrupt’ & ‘Democratise’ the travel industry by replacing the travel agent with a trustworthy fellow traveller.

How It Works?
1. Discover page - This is the landing page, here you can add friends & family, see our top influencers & also get inspired by current discoveries across the globe. Create your own Travel Network, based on ‘Trust’ & ‘Common travel Interests’.
2. Explore up to 5 destinations of your choice and have the flexibility of making comprehensive plans. The feed now comes from your closed network, thus instilling trust and confidence to go ahead and plan and book your trip.
3. Add multiple locations to your travel plan, seamlessly migrating from inspiration to travel planning. Assign dates and create ‘Truly Customised Itineraries’, catering to your travel interests.
4. Carry your travel plans on the go as you experience your destination.
5. Want to become a 'Travel Guru'? Post with us and earn exclusive badges and rewards.
6. Your travel discoveries are curated in your ‘World Travel Album’, for you to revisit your memories or help your network with recommendations.
descriptionShort: PYT: A Travel Ecosystem You Can Trust
